---
---

<section class="py-16 bg-slate-50 border-y border-slate-100 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      {/* Badge 1: Pago Seguro */}
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100/50 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-secondary-50 text-secondary-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-inner">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2" />
            <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Pago 100% Seguro</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
          Tus datos están protegidos bajo cifrado SSL. Transacción procesada de forma segura por Hotmart.
        </p>
      </div>

      {/* Badge 2: Garantía */}
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100/50 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-50 text-primary-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-inner">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Garantía de 7 Días</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
          Prueba los patrones sin riesgo. Si no cumplen tus expectativas, te devolvemos el 100% de tu dinero.
        </p>
      </div>

      {/* Badge 3: Acceso Inmediato */}
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100/50 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-inner">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4" />
            <polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10" />
            <line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Acceso Instantáneo</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
          Recibe un correo con el enlace para descargar el ebook en formato PDF inmediatamente tras el pago.
        </p>
      </div>

      {/* Badge 4: Soporte Premium */}
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100/50 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-50 text-green-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-inner">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M21 11.5a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9 3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1-7.6 4.7 8.38 8.38 0 0 1-3.8-.9L3 21l1.9-5.7a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9-3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1 4.7-7.6 8.38 8.38 0 0 1 3.8-.9h.5a8.48 8.48 0 0 1 8 8v.5z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Soporte por WhatsApp</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
          ¿Tienes dudas con algún punto? Escríbenos directamente y te ayudaremos en tu proceso de tejido.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
